    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "w4_text",
      "x": 35, "y": 437,
      "width": 270, "height": 90,
      "text": "4. FAN-OUT WRITES (parallelWrite)\ngoroutine per replica node — all N in parallel\nLocal node (fast path): storage.Put(key, siblings)\n  → per-key mutex sync.Map lock\nRemote nodes: rpc.RemotePut() → /internal/replicate",
      "originalText": "4. FAN-OUT WRITES (parallelWrite)\ngoroutine per replica node — all N in parallel\nLocal node (fast path): storage.Put(key, siblings)\n  → per-key mutex sync.Map lock\nRemote nodes: rpc.RemotePut() → /internal/replicate",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
