    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "w5_text",
      "x": 35, "y": 555,
      "width": 270, "height": 80,
      "text": "5. QUORUM EVALUATION\nsuccessCount ≥ W=2  → commit\nsuccessCount < W → sloppy quorum:\n  ring.GetExtendedPreferenceList() → overflow nodes\nIf still < W → return QuorumError",
      "originalText": "5. QUORUM EVALUATION\nsuccessCount ≥ W=2  → commit\nsuccessCount < W → sloppy quorum:\n  ring.GetExtendedPreferenceList() → overflow nodes\nIf still < W → return QuorumError",
