      "x": 35, "y": 663,
      "width": 270, "height": 80,
      "text": "6. SUCCESS AFTERMATH\ngo antiEntropy.OnKeyUpdate(key, siblings)\n  → MerkleTree.UpdateKey() incremental O(1)\nfailed remote write:\n  → hintedHandoff.StoreHint(nodeID, key, siblings)",
