      "id": "r3_text",
      "x": 395, "y": 329,
      "width": 270, "height": 90,
      "text": "3. FAN-OUT READS (parallelRead)\ngoroutine per replica — early return at R successes\nLocal (fast path): storage.GetRaw(key)\n  → tombstones visible for read repair\nRemote: rpc.RemoteGet() → /internal/read\n2s timeout per replica",
      "originalText": "3. FAN-OUT READS (parallelRead)\ngoroutine per replica — early return at R successes\nLocal (fast path): storage.GetRaw(key)\n  → tombstones visible for read repair\nRemote: rpc.RemoteGet() → /internal/read\n2s timeout per replica",
