      "id": "r4_text",
      "x": 395, "y": 447,
      "width": 270, "height": 80,
      "text": "4. QUORUM CHECK\nsuccessCount ≥ R=2?  → proceed\nIf not → return QuorumError\nMerge all siblings from all R responses:\n  allSiblings = union of each replica's SiblingSet",
      "originalText": "4. QUORUM CHECK\nsuccessCount ≥ R=2?  → proceed\nIf not → return QuorumError\nMerge all siblings from all R responses:\n  allSiblings = union of each replica's SiblingSet",
