    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "r5_text",
      "x": 395, "y": 555,
      "width": 270, "height": 80,
      "text": "5. SIBLING MERGE\nmergeAllSiblings():\n  for each s1: dominated by s2 if s1.VClock.HappensBefore(s2.VClock)\n  → keep only causally maximal siblings\n  → deduplicate by VClock.Equals()",
      "originalText": "5. SIBLING MERGE\nmergeAllSiblings():\n  for each s1: dominated by s2 if s1.VClock.HappensBefore(s2.VClock)\n  → keep only causally maximal siblings\n  → deduplicate by VClock.Equals()",
