      "x": 755, "y": 329,
      "width": 280, "height": 80,
      "text": "3. DIVERGENCE CHECK\nmyRoot == peerRoot  → skip (in sync)\nmyRoot != peerRoot  → scan bucket rangeIdx\n  Merkle tree: SHA-256 rolling hash\n  2^MerkleDepth buckets (default: 256)",
