      "x": 755, "y": 545,
      "width": 280, "height": 80,
      "text": "5. RECOVERY TRIGGER (EVENT-DRIVEN)\nFailureDetector.OnNodeRecovery callback\n  → coordinator.TriggerAntiEntropyWith(nodeID)\n  → TriggerWithPeer(nodeID) async goroutine\nFullSync: all 256 buckets pushed to recovered node",
      "originalText": "5. RECOVERY TRIGGER (EVENT-DRIVEN)\nFailureDetector.OnNodeRecovery callback\n  → coordinator.TriggerAntiEntropyWith(nodeID)\n  → TriggerWithPeer(nodeID) async goroutine\nFullSync: all 256 buckets pushed to recovered node",
